Description:
You arrive at a place with a mechanical crane that communicates with somewhere down the mountain.

This appears to be the way the nearby bazaar and cultists resupply. The crane is fully loaded and there is a supply ready to go up.

The problem is that to activate the crane, you have to enter a code using a keypad.
DescriptionAction: Lifting the cable manually would require a lot of force...
